welcome_message_body: "Welcome to North Laurel, a charming city known for its warm hospitality and beautiful scenery. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that our city has to offer during your stay."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tipton AAF Airport provides services for both commercial and military flights.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at BWI serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A offers flights to various domestic destinations.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B serves flights to popular international destinations.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free WiFi throughout the airport by connecting to the network.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Montgomery County Airport provides passengers with check-in, baggage claim, and boarding services for all flights.

terminals.name: Private Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The private aviation terminal at Montgomery County Airport offers services for private and corporate aircraft, including hangar space and VIP lounges.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy complimentary WiFi throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Lee Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Lee Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: Serves domestic flights for major airlines such as American Airlines, Delta, and United.

terminals.name: Terminal B
terminals.description: Serves domestic and international flights for various airlines including Alaska Airlines, Southwest, and JetBlue.

terminals.name: Terminal C
terminals.description: Serves domestic and international flights for major airlines such as American Airlines, Delta, and United.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport. No password required.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Glenn L Martin Airport handles all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Glenn L Martin Airport is used for shipping and receiving of goods and packages.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Potomac Airfield Airport is a small building with a check-in counter, security checkpoint, and a few gates for boarding.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: Potomac Airfield Airport also has a private terminal for private jet and charter flights. It offers a luxurious lounge and exclusive services for its passengers.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport, but may have limited signal strength in certain areas.
